1#,#1-ENG Major#,#Civil and Environmental Engineering#,#Engineering as Recommended by the Department of Civil and Environmental Engineering


gen_dept_reqs

core_subjects
Select one area of core coursework (54-66 units).
elect_eng
Students are required to take at least four Restricted Electives selected from subjects offered within or outside CEE to form a coherent program of study under supervision by CEE faculty.
